name: Fauna Flowers 04 - Jacaré Flower
description:
In the middle of the wetlands of Pantanal appears a rare prehistoric flower feared by all natives.
A wild species that has the ability to thrive on the soil and water. Nobody knows how it smells like. The last one who approached to try tasting its fragrance did not come back to tell. 
Piece of advice: do not take this one home with you.

Fauna Flowers is a collection made of animals mixed with plants in a new kind of magical possibilities. Discover this world where flowers can be a magnificent diversity of beautiful and unique creatures.
